when the country is free."

508
00:46:21,600 --> 00:46:24,280
"Mother!"

509
00:46:24,360 --> 00:46:32,760
"I'll take birth again,
when the country is free."

510
00:46:33,120 --> 00:46:37,720
"When the national flag will
is hoisted on the Himalayas."

511
00:46:37,800 --> 00:46:44,160
"Don't cry, mother.
You have many sons."

512
00:46:54,360 --> 00:47:00,160
"Just as one changes clothes.."

513
00:47:01,080 --> 00:47:05,640
"..the soul discards
the old body at death.."

514
00:47:06,360 --> 00:47:10,000
"..and takes on a new body.."

515
00:47:10,080 --> 00:47:15,840
"..to begin a new life."

516
00:47:19,280 --> 00:47:23,520
All's well!

517
00:47:28,560 --> 00:47:31,680
Sir, Kalyani has
sent this book for you.

518
00:47:33,800 --> 00:47:34,840
Ok.

519
00:47:45,920 --> 00:47:49,640
"The other day, I
became very restless.."

520
00:47:50,480 --> 00:47:52,480
"..while talking
about brother's death."

521
00:47:53,960 --> 00:47:55,880
"Brother meant everything to me."

522
00:47:57,040 --> 00:48:00,720
"I can't tell you.."

523
00:48:01,720 --> 00:48:04,200
"..how lonely I became after him."

524
00:48:05,680 --> 00:48:07,960
"I disliked everything in the world."

525
00:48:09,200 --> 00:48:14,920
"I would sit by the river and
stare at that place for hours.."

526
00:48:15,520 --> 00:48:18,640
"..where brother bid us goodbye."

527
00:48:23,840 --> 00:48:29,280
"Father tolerated the shock of
brother's death very calmly."

528
00:48:30,280 --> 00:48:33,480
"He used to try to keep
himself busy in work.."

529
00:48:34,200 --> 00:48:37,160
"..or in devotional poetry."

530
00:48:38,520 --> 00:48:41,840
"He used to stare at
brother's photo with sad eyes."

531
00:48:43,680 --> 00:48:46,000
"Without a drop of tear in his eyes."

532
00:48:49,480 --> 00:48:50,920
Hail God.

533
00:48:52,480 --> 00:48:53,880
Hail God.

534
00:49:08,280 --> 00:49:13,520
The sun never sets
on the British empire.

535
00:49:14,120 --> 00:49:15,560
What are you thinking, father?

536
00:49:17,760 --> 00:49:19,440
I'm thinking about you.

537
00:49:20,880 --> 00:49:24,440
Everyone says that I
should get you married now.

538
00:49:24,680 --> 00:49:26,880
This is what I don't like about you.

539
00:49:27,040 --> 00:49:30,520
Why do you listen to others?
I'll just study.

540
00:49:31,560 --> 00:49:33,880
What if I was your son?

541
00:49:34,240 --> 00:49:35,360
No.

542
00:49:36,240 --> 00:49:37,480
You're good as a daughter.

543
00:49:39,280 --> 00:49:41,120
God gave me a son.

544
00:49:42,560 --> 00:49:43,720
But in vain.

545
00:49:45,120 --> 00:49:47,880
Did he care about his old father?

546
00:49:49,640 --> 00:49:51,880
He ran to help the poor,
leaving his own house.

547
00:49:53,200 --> 00:49:55,680
And sacrificed his life for them.

548
00:49:57,960 --> 00:49:59,040
Whatever it is.

549
00:50:00,600 --> 00:50:02,280
His soul is resting in peace.

550
00:50:10,440 --> 00:50:13,040
Where did you run away again,
leaving your studies?

551
00:50:13,360 --> 00:50:16,320
I'll write to aunt that
you don't study at all!

552
00:50:16,520 --> 00:50:18,920
Sister, if I didn't study..

553
00:50:19,000 --> 00:50:21,200
..then how did I become
the monitor of my class?

554
00:50:32,520 --> 00:50:35,600
Why did you bring all this here?

555
00:50:35,960 --> 00:50:38,520
Had you called me, I would've
come there and had breakfast.

556
00:50:38,600 --> 00:50:42,240
Rubbish! If I called you at 8,
you would've come after 10!

557
00:50:43,720 --> 00:50:47,160
What to do, dear? I
can't work like I used to.

558
00:50:47,440 --> 00:50:50,120
I get tired soon. Keep it.

559
00:50:56,120 --> 00:50:58,600
Oh, God! A bomb blast again!

560
00:50:58,880 --> 00:51:00,160
Where, Mr. Mishra!

561
00:51:00,280 --> 00:51:02,960
A 14 year old boy in Muzzafarpur..

562
00:51:03,040 --> 00:51:07,160
..threw a bomb on a British magistrate,
who was sitting on a carriage.

563
00:51:07,360 --> 00:51:09,000
What's the world come to?

564
00:51:09,080 --> 00:51:13,680
Nowadays children start
making bombs at a very small age!

565
00:51:13,880 --> 00:51:16,680
There was peace in our village.

566
00:51:16,920 --> 00:51:21,280
But from the time that revolutionary
boy has been house arrested here,

567
00:51:21,360 --> 00:51:24,520
I'm afraid bombs will start
exploding in our village too!

568
00:51:24,680 --> 00:51:27,320
Looking at him, I get very scared!

569
00:51:27,880 --> 00:51:31,280
Who're you talking about?
That Vikas Ghosh?

570
00:51:31,720 --> 00:51:34,800
I saw him at inspector
Hussain's house the other day.

571
00:51:35,280 --> 00:51:37,040
He seemed to be very innocent.

572
00:51:39,040 --> 00:51:44,600
Don't praise such a boy,
or else you'll be fired.

573
00:51:44,920 --> 00:51:47,400
You should stay away from them.

574
00:51:47,640 --> 00:51:55,200
"Next to the Jamuna river,
I met Kanhaiya."

575
00:51:58,320 --> 00:52:00,400
Who did you meet?

576
00:52:01,160 --> 00:52:05,400
Not me, Shobha, but
Goddess Radha did! - Really?

577
00:52:05,480 --> 00:52:08,440
Where are you coming from?
- Aunt was not well.

578
00:52:08,560 --> 00:52:11,120
I came to see her. I'm
going home now. - Ok, wait.

579
00:52:11,200 --> 00:52:14,000
Even I've to go there.
Sister Prabha will tutor me.

580
00:52:14,080 --> 00:52:17,360
I'll inform father
and then come with you.

581
00:52:18,440 --> 00:52:21,480
I came so far while talking.
I'm going.

582
00:52:21,600 --> 00:52:24,000
I'll definitely give you my
in-laws' address before leaving.

583
00:52:24,080 --> 00:52:25,600
Do write to me!

584
00:52:31,320 --> 00:52:34,040
Listen! Come here!

585
00:52:34,360 --> 00:52:36,200
The way to the river..

586
00:52:43,600 --> 00:52:46,000
Why did they run
away on seeing that man?

587
00:52:46,120 --> 00:52:49,880
It's obvious. Don't you
know who he is.. - Who?

588
00:52:50,320 --> 00:52:52,720
He's the revolutionary Vikas Ghosh..

589
00:52:52,840 --> 00:52:55,360
..who's under house
arrest in this village.

590
00:52:55,640 --> 00:52:58,040
It's police's strict order
that no one should talk to him.

591
00:52:59,960 --> 00:53:01,840
He has a unique smile.

592
00:53:02,560 --> 00:53:07,120
You find it unique!
I'm scared! I'm leaving.

593
00:53:07,200 --> 00:53:09,480
You better leave too.

594
00:53:34,000 --> 00:53:35,920
Sister Prabha.
- Yes, Kalyani.

595
00:53:36,000 --> 00:53:39,280
I'm done with my studies.
I'll go home now.

596
00:53:41,400 --> 00:53:43,760
How'll you go? It's
raining so heavily.

597
00:53:43,840 --> 00:53:47,440
I doubt it'll stop.
You stay here tonight.

598
00:53:47,600 --> 00:53:50,360
No. If I don't reach home,
dad will get worried.

599
00:53:50,480 --> 00:53:53,560
I'll ask the peon of
the school to inform him.

600
00:53:53,760 --> 00:53:55,600
You'll fall sick if you get drenched.

601
00:53:55,840 --> 00:53:58,080
Come, help me in the kitchen.

602
00:54:15,240 --> 00:54:16,320
What's the news, Tarun?

603
00:54:16,440 --> 00:54:18,720
You've been assigned
an important work.

604
00:54:18,920 --> 00:54:22,120
You know that Vikas from our
group is under house arrest here.

605
00:54:22,200 --> 00:54:24,640
You'll have to deliver a
letter to him by tomorrow.

606
00:54:25,360 --> 00:54:28,600
It's important. He
should get it by tomorrow.

607
00:54:28,760 --> 00:54:31,760
Fine, I will. But why did
you come so late at night?

608
00:54:31,840 --> 00:54:33,120
I came long back..

609
00:54:33,200 --> 00:54:36,120
..but there's tight police surveillance
in this village due to Vikas.

610
00:54:36,280 --> 00:54:38,160
That's why I'm hiding in the jungle.

611
00:54:55,680 --> 00:54:58,240
You're still awake.

612
00:54:58,960 --> 00:55:00,480
You must've heard everything then.

613
00:55:00,920 --> 00:55:03,160
Sister, was it your brother?

614
00:55:03,400 --> 00:55:07,800
Yes. Look, don't
tell anyone about him.

615
00:55:11,680 --> 00:55:16,000
Kalyani, everything is ruined!
I think Tarun is caught!

616
00:55:16,920 --> 00:55:19,080
The police might be here any moment.

617
00:55:21,240 --> 00:55:25,320
You take this letter and run away.

618
00:55:25,400 --> 00:55:27,400
Give this letter to
Vikas at any cost tomorrow.

619
00:55:27,480 --> 00:55:29,920
Me?
- Yes. No one will suspect you.

620
00:55:30,720 --> 00:55:32,600
Go. Hurry up.

621
00:55:34,920 --> 00:55:39,800
Not from here. Go from the backyard,
through the jungle.

622
00:56:03,440 --> 00:56:05,160
Who came here?
- No one.

623
00:56:05,320 --> 00:56:07,400
Someone definitely
came here! We'll search!

624
00:56:07,600 --> 00:56:10,680
As you wish.
- Go! Search the entire place!

625
00:56:55,840 --> 00:56:58,160
Constable!
- What?

626
00:56:58,800 --> 00:57:01,520
Let me pluck some flowers from there!
- No!

627
00:57:03,040 --> 00:57:06,240
Actually, there's a
prayer back at our place.

628
00:57:06,320 --> 00:57:09,880
And I need are these
flowers to worship god..

629
00:57:09,960 --> 00:57:11,600
..or else the
prayers can't be conducted!

630
00:57:11,680 --> 00:57:15,120
I searched everywhere, but
I didn't find such flowers!

631
00:57:16,080 --> 00:57:19,600
Please!
- No one is allowed to go in!

632
00:57:20,280 --> 00:57:25,160
You're very sweet! I'll just take 2
flowers! - Where have you come from?

633
00:57:25,600 --> 00:57:28,840
Don't you know that I'm
the post master's daughter?

634
00:57:28,920 --> 00:57:31,000
Mr. Sadashiv's daughter?
- Yes!

635
00:57:31,080 --> 00:57:33,160
Okay. Pluck them.

636
00:58:11,400 --> 00:58:13,080
Greetings, inspector.

637
00:58:19,560 --> 00:58:23,080
Greetings.
- Welcome, sir! Have a seat!

638
00:58:23,920 --> 00:58:25,320
What's the matter?

639
00:58:25,440 --> 00:58:28,440
You've surrounded my
house with barbwires.

640
00:58:28,520 --> 00:58:31,200
You've appointed two
Constables to guard my house.

641
00:58:31,280 --> 00:58:33,600
Why am I being
honored all of a sudden?

642
00:58:33,800 --> 00:58:38,160
We'll have to. You're a special guest!

643
00:58:38,840 --> 00:58:42,200
Are you completely unaware
of last night's incident?

644
00:58:43,640 --> 00:58:45,480
I heard the sounds of crackers.

645
00:58:45,560 --> 00:58:49,520
And those sounds
have ruined our slumber!

646
00:58:50,440 --> 00:58:52,760
No!
- Give it to me!

647
00:58:55,560 --> 00:58:58,360
You appointed a dumb and deaf servant.

648
00:58:58,600 --> 00:59:00,360
I'm not allowed to
talk to the villagers.

649
00:59:00,440 --> 00:59:03,160
From your new arrangement, it
seems like I can't even go out.

650
00:59:03,240 --> 00:59:08,640
No. After last night's incident, we
had to take precautionary measures.

651
00:59:08,880 --> 00:59:10,720
But I'm facing problems.

652
00:59:10,920 --> 00:59:16,080
I realize your problems,
but I can't do anything.

653
00:59:16,680 --> 00:59:21,160
Yes, I can permit you to talk,
not to the villagers..

654
00:59:21,440 --> 00:59:26,680
..but the government officials.
I won't mind that.

655
00:59:27,040 --> 00:59:30,480
Thank you so much.
- Ok, I'll take your leave.

656
00:59:31,320 --> 00:59:34,000
Come to the police station
for the attendance. - Ok.

657
00:59:45,000 --> 00:59:48,440
It's ok! She's the
post master's daughter!

658
00:59:52,040 --> 00:59:54,680
How long will you stand
holding all this? Keep it.

659
00:59:55,440 --> 00:59:58,400
Let me complete my work
and then have breakfast.

660
00:59:58,760 --> 01:00:02,160
You finish your work. I'm
standing here till then.

661
01:00:05,680 --> 01:00:07,680
Can I come in?
- Who's it?

662
01:00:09,440 --> 01:00:11,920
Come. It's you!

663
01:00:12,680 --> 01:00:14,600
Greetings.

664
01:00:17,680 --> 01:00:20,360
Please sit.
- Yes.

665
01:00:20,760 --> 01:00:23,280
I couldn't find the
courage to meet you.

666
01:00:23,720 --> 01:00:27,680
Now that inspector has permitted me,
so I came to trouble you.

667
01:00:27,760 --> 01:00:30,880
It's no trouble at all. Sit.

668
01:00:31,120 --> 01:00:34,560
I'll order tea.
- Yes, I'll definitely have tea.

669
01:00:34,880 --> 01:00:37,880
Won't I get pudding to eat?

670
01:00:37,960 --> 01:00:41,960
What? Yes. - Sorry! As soon
as I saw this, I'm hungry!

671
01:00:42,640 --> 01:00:46,920
Gopal, ask Kalyani to send tea
and pudding for Mr. Vikas. - Yes.

672
01:00:49,320 --> 01:00:51,240
Don't mind my being informal.
- No.

673
01:00:51,480 --> 01:00:54,960
It's a rule that the host
always force their guests to eat..

674
01:00:55,040 --> 01:00:56,480
..but the guest refuses.

675
01:00:56,800 --> 01:00:59,080
But our society is different.

676
01:00:59,360 --> 01:01:01,840
We hardly get good food to eat.

677
01:01:02,000 --> 01:01:04,720
That's why whenever
I see such a thing..

678
01:01:04,840 --> 01:01:06,280
..I don't feel like leaving it!

679
01:01:09,000 --> 01:01:12,040
Gopal, take. You give him.

680
01:01:12,120 --> 01:01:15,160
No! I'm scared!
- Why? Go!

681
01:01:17,600 --> 01:01:20,920
The inspector was saying that
you've a number of poetries.

682
01:01:21,320 --> 01:01:24,240
If you don't mind, can I come
and listen to them sometimes?

683
01:01:24,320 --> 01:01:27,640
Yes, absolutely! I'll be glad!

684
01:01:28,040 --> 01:01:31,280
Why are you standing there?
Keep the snacks here.

685
01:01:34,760 --> 01:01:37,000
Who's this boy?
- He's the son of my widowed sister.

686
01:01:37,360 --> 01:01:38,640
He lives with me and studies here.

687
01:01:38,760 --> 01:01:40,840
The pudding's very tasty!
Who cooked it?

688
01:01:40,960 --> 01:01:42,240
My daughter, Kalyani.

689
01:01:43,200 --> 01:01:45,120
She was standing here when you came.

690
01:01:45,360 --> 01:01:47,000
I forgot to introduce you.
- Never mind.

691
01:01:47,080 --> 01:01:49,560
Gopla. Call your sister.
- Ok.

692
01:01:52,080 --> 01:01:54,840
Sister!

693
01:01:56,480 --> 01:01:57,720
Uncle is calling you.

694
01:01:58,720 --> 01:02:00,840
Tell him that I'm going for a bath.
- Okay.

695
01:02:25,800 --> 01:02:27,520
Who gave that letter to you?

696
01:02:29,480 --> 01:02:30,680
Sister Prabha.

697
01:02:31,040 --> 01:02:33,680
Is she Prakash's elder sister?
- Yes.

698
01:02:34,240 --> 01:02:36,720
When did Prakash come to
this village? - Mr. Vikas!

699
01:02:38,680 --> 01:02:42,280
The pudding was so tasty that..

700
01:02:42,400 --> 01:02:44,960
..I'll have to come to
your place again for that!

701
01:02:46,280 --> 01:02:48,280
She was the post
master's daughter, wasn't she?

702
01:02:48,680 --> 01:02:53,120
By the riverside! Wow!
- I forgot my way and came here.

703
01:02:53,200 --> 01:02:55,360
But don't forget your
attendance in the evening.

704
01:02:55,640 --> 01:02:59,240
How can I forget in
your presence, inspector?

705
01:03:15,000 --> 01:03:16,440
Sister!

706
01:03:18,080 --> 01:03:20,640
Where are you?
- See!

707
01:03:20,720 --> 01:03:22,080
Oh gosh! I was scared!

708
01:03:23,080 --> 01:03:25,240
I scared you!
- Yes!

709
01:03:25,320 --> 01:03:28,520
Aren't you scared of Mr. Vikas?

710
01:03:28,920 --> 01:03:30,440
Why?

711
01:03:30,680 --> 01:03:32,520
I'm very scared of him!

712
01:03:32,760 --> 01:03:34,720
When he comes this time..

713
01:03:34,800 --> 01:03:38,320
..ask him the technique of making
bombs. - I'll definitely teach you!

714
01:03:38,400 --> 01:03:40,840
Oh gosh!
- Wait! Don't run away!

715
01:03:43,600 --> 01:03:46,840
Is your dad at home?
- Yes. Come.

716
01:03:52,320 --> 01:03:56,000
"O night, today you
decide my fate."

717
01:03:57,080 --> 01:04:01,800
"Let me catch
a glimpse of my beloved."

718
01:04:02,680 --> 01:04:06,080
"And my life
will be successful."

719
01:04:06,520 --> 01:04:09,360
"I feel like I've
the entire world."

720
01:04:09,640 --> 01:04:11,240
Wonderful.

721
01:04:11,680 --> 01:04:13,240
You've heard very little, dear.

722
01:04:13,560 --> 01:04:15,120
Reading this poetry
makes you feel blissful.

723
01:04:16,600 --> 01:04:17,840
Sit, dear.

724
01:04:18,800 --> 01:04:20,960
Your dad recites such
good devotional poetry.

725
01:04:21,320 --> 01:04:22,760
You might know it as well.

726
01:04:23,000 --> 01:04:24,480
She does recite it sometimes.

727
01:04:24,800 --> 01:04:27,720
That's what I wanted to know!
You must sing too.

728
01:04:28,880 --> 01:04:31,480
Not worth singing in front of anyone.
- She's got a sweet voice..

729
01:04:32,000 --> 01:04:34,040
..but she didn't get
a chance to learn.

730
01:04:34,240 --> 01:04:37,600
But this is not any singing
competition. Sing as you can.

731
01:04:38,080 --> 01:04:40,120
I spoke impolitely to her!

732
01:04:40,400 --> 01:04:44,040
So what? She's younger to you.

733
01:04:50,320 --> 01:04:54,520
"Since the time you
came in my life, beloved"

734
01:04:55,360 --> 01:04:59,520
"Since the time you came
in my life, beloved.."

735
01:04:59,760 --> 01:05:04,040
"..my life has become beautiful."

736
01:05:04,680 --> 01:05:08,640
"You read my eyes and
understood what's in my heart."

737
01:05:09,040 --> 01:05:13,560
"I shouldn't have met you."

738
01:05:13,640 --> 01:05:17,800
"Since the time you
came in my life, beloved"

739
01:05:31,440 --> 01:05:35,920
"You fell in love with
this dusky looking girl."

740
01:05:36,000 --> 01:05:38,240
"You fell in love with
this dusky looking girl."

741
01:05:38,320 --> 01:05:41,720
"When I saw you and
peered in your eyes."

742
01:05:42,720 --> 01:05:47,200
"When I saw you and
peered in your eyes.."

743
01:05:47,280 --> 01:05:51,480
"..my eyes looked
adorned without the kohl."

744
01:05:51,600 --> 01:05:55,920
"Since the time you came
in my life, beloved.."

745
01:05:56,000 --> 01:06:00,560
"..my life has become beautiful."

746
01:06:14,200 --> 01:06:18,760
"I sit at the shore like crazy Radha."

747
01:06:18,840 --> 01:06:21,200
"I sit at the shore like crazy Radha."

748
01:06:21,280 --> 01:06:24,480
"I return without fetching water."

749
01:06:25,520 --> 01:06:28,280
"I return without fetching water."

750
01:06:28,360 --> 01:06:34,080
"It's a strange kind of illness."

751
01:06:34,480 --> 01:06:38,840
"Since the time you came
in my life, beloved.."

