'..and went to fetch water.'

807
01:11:10,000 --> 01:11:14,040
'When I came back, I
saw that he was dead.'

808
01:11:14,360 --> 01:11:17,840
'The one who wanted to see
the country free, had died.'

809
01:11:18,840 --> 01:11:21,200
'Suddenly, I heard 'Hands up'.'

810
01:11:22,200 --> 01:11:26,240
'The police found us due to the
drops of blood on the ground.'

811
01:11:27,880 --> 01:11:30,960
'I was sleeping in prison.'

812
01:11:33,720 --> 01:11:35,760
'Suddenly someone woke me.'

813
