lady was, who got me released".'

818
01:12:03,320 --> 01:12:06,560
'He told me that she was
the inspector's wife.'

819
01:12:07,200 --> 01:12:08,160
'I was shocked.'

820
01:12:08,400 --> 01:12:11,160
'Later when that man told me that..'

821
01:12:11,240 --> 01:12:14,840
'..she has helped a
lot of revolutionaries.'

822
01:12:15,600 --> 01:12:16,960
'I was amazed.'

823
01:12:17,320 --> 01:12:20,520
'After seeing motherly love
in that inspector's wife..'

824
01:12:21,840 --> 01:12:24,320
'..my opinion about women changed.'

825
01:12:24,840 --> 01:12:27,960
'There's no need for
women to be like men.'

826
01:12:28,760 --> 01:12:31,000
'They can help us from home.'

827
