to register my attendance. - Wait.

828
01:12:41,520 --> 01:12:43,080
I'll light the lamp.

829
01:12:49,320 --> 01:12:51,120
Who named you Kalyani?

830
01:12:52,320 --> 01:12:54,560
I don't know. I think brother did.

831
01:12:55,240 --> 01:12:56,480
It suits you.

832
01:12:56,920 --> 01:13:02,560
Others' names are just for namesake,
but yours reflects your identity.

833
01:13:03,440 --> 01:13:05,160
You're really Kalyani (well-wisher).

834
01:13:08,480 --> 01:13:10,800
It is said that the eyes
reflect what's in your mind.

835
01:13:11,920 --> 01:13:15,880
