Let it stop raining, you
can leave then. Come in.

887
01:19:16,280 --> 01:19:17,520
I'm thirsty.

888
01:19:18,360 --> 01:19:19,560
I'll get water.

889
01:20:14,120 --> 01:20:15,920
I.. Did I fall asleep?

890
01:20:16,120 --> 01:20:19,440
I feel asleep. How are you now?

891
01:20:20,280 --> 01:20:21,320
I'm fine.

892
01:20:27,320 --> 01:20:28,520
Mr. Vikas!

893
01:20:29,640 --> 01:20:31,080
Someone is calling you.

894
01:20:32,240 --> 01:20:33,640
What will we do now?

895
01:20:34,920 --> 01:20:36,480
Mr. Vikas!

896
01:20:37,480 --> 01:20:38,720
Don't worry. I'll see.

897
01:20:40,400 --> 01:20:41,680
Mr. Vikas!

898
01:20:52,240 --> 01:20:58,240
What you did was bad!
Anyway, come on.

899
01:20:58,880 --> 01:21:00,200
Where's the post master?

900
01:21:00,280 --> 01:21:05,680
Yes, call him. Explain to him
that decent people live here!

901
01:21:05,760 --> 01:21:11,440
Instead, send her to some brothel..
- Hey! Mind your tongue!

902
01:21:13,680 --> 01:21:15,960
I won't tolerate my
wife's humiliation!

903
01:21:17,560 --> 01:21:20,280
Your wife?
- Yes.

904
01:21:20,480 --> 01:21:26,160
Sir, ask him when and how he
got married.. - Keep quiet!

905
01:21:27,600 --> 01:21:30,160
Excuse me.

906
01:21:35,400 --> 01:21:39,160
Come. Take blessings from your dad.

907
01:21:41,680 --> 01:21:43,320
Don't hesitate.

908
01:21:46,720 --> 01:21:47,840
Come with me.

909
01:22:09,080 --> 01:22:15,400
We want your blessings. Please
bless us that we live happily.

910
01:22:19,760 --> 01:22:23,520
I'm solely responsible for
whatever happened today.

911
01:22:26,880 --> 01:22:28,160
Believe me.

912
01:22:28,800 --> 01:22:31,880
I'm not marrying her just to
save you from getting humiliated.

913
01:22:32,080 --> 01:22:33,560
I really love..

914
01:22:39,880 --> 01:22:42,440
I.. never imagined that..

915
01:22:42,520 --> 01:22:45,960
..I'd have to come to you
for her in such circumstances.

916
01:22:56,880 --> 01:22:58,040
The police are waiting for me.

917
01:23:07,000 --> 01:23:08,520
I need time to think.

918
01:23:49,400 --> 01:23:51,760
Is your dad not well?

919
01:23:54,560 --> 01:23:56,200
Go and serve tea to dad.

920
01:23:56,280 --> 01:24:01,120
Why? You serve him everyday.
Why should I go today?

921
01:24:01,840 --> 01:24:03,640
No. You serve him.

922
01:24:04,120 --> 01:24:08,600
Wonder what's wrong with everyone!
Everyone's upset! Give it!

923
01:24:18,400 --> 01:24:22,480
There's an order from Sadar that
Vikas has to be sent there today.

924
01:24:23,360 --> 01:24:27,240
He wanted to meet you
before going. I allowed him.

925
01:24:28,840 --> 01:24:33,760
What do I do? I can't find
any solution, inspector.

926
01:24:34,280 --> 01:24:37,080
I can understand
your condition, brother.

927
01:24:37,440 --> 01:24:41,600
But I think you should get
Kalyani married to Vikas.

928
01:24:42,520 --> 01:24:46,920
But he's not well settled. - It's
the question of dignity right now.

929
01:24:47,200 --> 01:24:51,440
If you refuse, then the
villagers will start taunting.

930
01:24:51,840 --> 01:24:59,160
Honestly speaking these
revolutionaries keep their word.

931
01:25:00,440 --> 01:25:05,520
I think the restrictions on
him will also be lifted soon.

932
01:25:06,520 --> 01:25:10,160
I suggest don't hesitate
in getting them married.

933
01:25:11,000 --> 01:25:15,440
The rest is your decision.
I'll take your leave.

934
01:25:22,480 --> 01:25:24,520
Don't you want to say anything?

935
01:25:27,680 --> 01:25:34,680
I'd be satisfied if I could hear you
say that I didn't make any mistake.

936
01:25:47,320 --> 01:25:50,640
Here's my address. Write to me.

937
01:26:07,160 --> 01:26:12,160
The police are waiting for me.
I have to go to Sadar.

938
01:26:13,400 --> 01:26:14,720
Did you think about us?

939
01:26:16,000 --> 01:26:17,080
Yes, son.

940
01:26:18,520 --> 01:26:20,680
I've decided to get
Kalyani married to you.

941
01:26:22,960 --> 01:26:27,680
Vikas, I've no one else in
this world, besides Kalyani.

942
01:26:29,200 --> 01:26:30,680
Don't ever hurt her.

943
01:26:41,320 --> 01:26:42,440
Mr. Vikas.

944
01:26:48,800 --> 01:26:50,000
Listen.

945
01:27:15,400 --> 01:27:17,000
Mr. Vikas, hurry up.

946
01:28:14,360 --> 01:28:16,480
How are you, Sadashiv?

947
01:28:16,880 --> 01:28:18,960
Have a seat, doctor.

948
01:28:19,400 --> 01:28:23,480
That school teacher Raghu was
saying that you've slowed down.

949
01:28:23,840 --> 01:28:27,520
Yes. I've been ill since a few days

950
01:28:28,520 --> 01:28:31,240
Poor teacher does my work.

951
01:28:31,360 --> 01:28:35,120
I was busy too. After a long time,
I've managed to come.

952
01:28:35,560 --> 01:28:38,000
Did Mr. Vikas write to you?

953
01:28:39,240 --> 01:28:42,000
Yes, 2 months after he left.

954
01:28:43,280 --> 01:28:46,120
He wrote that the
police have released him..

955
01:28:46,560 --> 01:28:48,400
..but he's down with malaria.

956
01:28:49,440 --> 01:28:51,240
He'll come here as
soon as he gets well.

957
01:28:52,960 --> 01:28:55,000
But 2 months have passed.

958
01:28:56,080 --> 01:28:59,040
Neither did he come,
nor did his letter.

959
01:28:59,240 --> 01:29:00,880
Didn't you write to him?

960
01:29:01,520 --> 01:29:06,080
Four times, but he didn't reply.

961
01:29:06,960 --> 01:29:08,680
That's strange.

962
01:29:09,640 --> 01:29:12,880
It'd be better if
Kalyani got married soon.

963
01:29:13,840 --> 01:29:18,000
The villagers are gossiping.
They're spreading strange rumors.

964
01:29:18,200 --> 01:29:23,120
I think you should get
Kalyani married to some other boy.

965
01:29:23,400 --> 01:29:25,080
It will shut everyone up.

966
01:29:25,560 --> 01:29:30,000
I can't commit a sin in
order to shut everyone's mouth!

967
01:29:30,840 --> 01:29:33,440
Is marriage everything in life?

968
01:29:35,120 --> 01:29:37,960
Vikas has accepted her as his wife..

969
01:29:38,760 --> 01:29:40,240
..and even I agreed.

970
01:29:41,400 --> 01:29:45,600
I believe that Kalyani
and Vikas are married.

971
01:29:51,840 --> 01:29:54,200
Kalyani, there's a letter.

972
01:29:55,600 --> 01:29:56,720
My letter!

973
01:29:58,040 --> 01:29:59,720
It's not for you.

974
01:29:59,960 --> 01:30:04,560
The letter that you sent
to Mr. Vikas has returned.

975
01:30:07,640 --> 01:30:09,200
I hope dad didn't see.

976
01:30:09,280 --> 01:30:12,880
No. I kept it with me.

977
01:30:42,400 --> 01:30:44,560
Kalyani, listen.

978
01:30:46,760 --> 01:30:48,360
Is your marriage date fixed?

979
01:30:49,560 --> 01:30:54,200
I don't know. - You don't
know when your marriage is!

980
01:30:54,920 --> 01:30:57,200
But do invite us!

981
01:30:57,360 --> 01:31:00,760
Invitation for what?
She's already married!

982
01:31:01,000 --> 01:31:02,560
She won't marry again!

983
01:31:29,960 --> 01:31:31,560
Did you call me, sister?

984
01:31:32,880 --> 01:31:33,960
Yes.

985
01:31:34,640 --> 01:31:37,760
Did Vikas reply to your letter?

986
01:31:39,000 --> 01:31:42,160
No. My letter came back.

987
01:31:43,520 --> 01:31:45,480
He doesn't live on that address.

988
01:31:47,080 --> 01:31:50,120
Tarun wrote the same to me.

989
01:31:51,040 --> 01:31:53,080
He sent a bad news too.

990
01:31:54,520 --> 01:31:55,800
How do I tell you?

991
01:31:57,000 --> 01:31:58,600
You'll be very upset.

992
01:32:00,280 --> 01:32:03,040
I'm used to enduring sorrows now.

993
01:32:04,720 --> 01:32:05,880
Tell me.

994
01:32:07,040 --> 01:32:10,920
He has written that Vikas
doesn't live in Lucknow.

995
01:32:11,760 --> 01:32:14,680
He works in Patna. And..

996
01:32:16,800 --> 01:32:18,240
He got married.

997
01:32:21,080 --> 01:32:24,840
Kalyani, women are
born to endure sorrows.

998
01:32:25,280 --> 01:32:27,000
Make yourself strong.

999
01:32:32,400 --> 01:32:34,240
I'm very strong.

1000
01:32:44,240 --> 01:32:47,600
We've been listening since
months that he'll write to you!

1001
01:32:48,000 --> 01:32:50,960
Don't puzzle us now! - It's a lie!

1002
01:32:51,560 --> 01:32:53,880
He neither wrote to them,
nor will he ever write!

1003
01:32:54,320 --> 01:32:55,960
He's gone!

1004
01:32:57,840 --> 01:33:01,760
What can I do if we
didn't write to us?

1005
01:33:01,840 --> 01:33:03,520
Why are you asking us?

1006
01:33:03,800 --> 01:33:06,480
Did you ask us
before calling him home..

1007
01:33:06,720 --> 01:33:12,960
..and reciting romantic
poetry in front of your daughter?

1008
01:33:14,480 --> 01:33:15,760
Please keep quiet!

1009
01:33:15,840 --> 01:33:19,120
How many can you stop? The
entire village is saying this!

1010
01:33:19,320 --> 01:33:22,360
Bear the consequences of your deeds!
- Fine.

1011
01:33:22,760 --> 01:33:26,880
I did what I wanted to. And
now you do what you want to!

1012
01:33:27,320 --> 01:33:30,640
This is a government office!
If you people threaten me here..

1013
01:33:30,840 --> 01:33:33,440
..I'll complain to the police!
- Yes! Go!

1014
01:33:33,720 --> 01:33:37,600
We'll see how you live in this
locality with your daughter!

1015
01:33:37,880 --> 01:33:39,760
Won't we?
- Yes!

1016
01:33:48,160 --> 01:33:49,240
Kalyani.

1017
01:33:55,320 --> 01:33:56,400
Kalyani.

1018
01:33:57,240 --> 01:33:59,760
I can't find a clean drape.
Didn't the washer-man come?

1019
01:34:01,120 --> 01:34:02,840
Answer me!
Didn't the washer-man come?

1020
01:34:04,800 --> 01:34:06,800
Gopal!

1021
01:34:06,960 --> 01:34:08,120
Yes.

1022
01:34:08,200 --> 01:34:10,800
Go and get my washed
drape from the washer man!

1023
01:34:12,400 --> 01:34:14,400
Sister sent me to him yesterday..

1024
01:34:14,680 --> 01:34:17,120
..but he said that the
villagers have threatened him.

1025
01:34:17,400 --> 01:34:19,640
That's why he won't
wash our clothes.

1026
01:34:21,640 --> 01:34:22,720
You go.

1027
01:34:31,160 --> 01:34:34,360
Kalyani, listen. You
write to Vikas today.

1028
01:34:35,040 --> 01:34:38,560
No. I won't.
- Why?

1029
01:34:39,720 --> 01:34:40,760
Fine.

1030
01:34:41,800 --> 01:34:42,920
I will.

1031
01:34:43,440 --> 01:34:45,720
No. You don't write either.

1032
01:34:46,200 --> 01:34:49,040
You won't write, neither will
you let me. What do you want to do?

1033
01:34:49,800 --> 01:34:54,000
People insult me in my own house
and you want me to keep quiet!

1034
01:34:54,560 --> 01:34:56,680
I get so humiliated because of you!

1035
01:34:57,080 --> 01:34:59,880
Either you leave this house,
or I'll leave it!

1036
01:35:12,840 --> 01:35:15,920
'Dad, I'm leaving this house.'

1037
01:35:17,160 --> 01:35:20,200
'But, trust me I'm
not angry with you.'

1038
01:35:20,880 --> 01:35:23,200
'I'm going because I don't
have any other alternative.'

1039
01:35:24,400 --> 01:35:27,560
'I can't see the
villagers insulting you.'

1040
01:35:28,480 --> 01:35:32,160
'Until I'm here,
your sorrows will grow.'

1041
01:35:32,600 --> 01:35:33,520
'And I..

1042
01:35:34,400 --> 01:35:39,160
..can't see you sad because of me.'

1043
01:35:41,360 --> 01:35:45,440
'Had I told you this before,
you wouldn't have allowed me.'

1044
01:35:46,680 --> 01:35:49,960
'Perhaps, I wouldn't even feel
like going after seeing you.'

1045
01:35:51,040 --> 01:35:55,200
'That's why I'm leaving at night,
without informing you.'

1046
01:35:56,440 --> 01:35:57,480
'Dad..

1047
01:35:58,280 --> 01:35:59,560
'Don't search for me.'

1048
01:36:00,520 --> 01:36:02,160
'Don't worry about me either.'

1049
01:36:03,520 --> 01:36:08,720
'Your blessings will
always protect me.'

1050
01:36:41,200 --> 01:36:42,240
'Dad..

1051
01:36:43,520 --> 01:36:44,880
..please forgive me.'

1052
01:37:55,400 --> 01:38:05,080
"Someone is calling
you out every time."

1053
01:38:06,920 --> 01:38:14,400
"Someone is calling
you out every time."

1054
01:38:14,960 --> 01:38:22,600
"The one who goes
there never returns."

1055
01:38:22,680 --> 01:38:29,960
"Someone tell me what secret is this?"

1056
01:38:31,160 --> 01:38:37,320
"O traveller, come back if possible."

1057
01:38:38,080 --> 01:38:45,320
"Don't forget this bank, this path."

1058
01:38:46,440 --> 01:38:52,840
"O traveller, come back if possible."

1059
01:39:04,040 --> 01:39:05,600
See who it is.

1060
01:39:08,480 --> 01:39:09,600
It's you!

1061
01:39:10,640 --> 01:39:12,160
Where's your luggage?

1062
01:39:12,840 --> 01:39:15,800
Who have you come with?
- I've come alone.

1063
01:39:17,800 --> 01:39:19,400
Ok. Come in.

1064
01:39:20,360 --> 01:39:24,160
My dad told me about
you a few days back.

1065
01:39:25,880 --> 01:39:27,960
Why did you come all of a sudden,
without informing?

1066
01:39:29,160 --> 01:39:31,120
I couldn't live in
the village anymore.

1067
01:39:32,040 --> 01:39:33,960
I thought of staying
with you for a few days.

1068
01:39:34,200 --> 01:39:36,000
Is there no news about Mr. Vikas?

1069
01:39:38,960 --> 01:39:40,720
Why did you leave
the village suddenly?

1070
01:39:44,880 --> 01:39:49,200
Everyone started humiliating
my old father because of me.

1071
01:39:49,840 --> 01:39:51,480
I couldn't endure that.

1072
01:39:58,520 --> 01:40:02,560
Who's she?
- My friend, from our village.

1073
01:40:04,520 --> 01:40:08,400
It's ok. Don't touch. You've
come from outside. I've to pray.

1074
01:40:08,920 --> 01:40:10,400
Sit, Kalyani.

1075
01:40:11,080 --> 01:40:13,760
Daughter-in-law. She's the daughter..

1076
01:40:13,880 --> 01:40:15,760
..of the post master of your village?

1077
01:40:15,880 --> 01:40:18,960
Your dad was talking
about her, wasn't he?

1078
01:40:19,080 --> 01:40:21,280
There was a scandal in
your village because of her..

1079
01:40:21,400 --> 01:40:22,600
Mother, come here.

1080
01:40:22,720 --> 01:40:25,120
You shouldn't say all
this in front of her.

1081
01:40:25,680 --> 01:40:30,040
Look, I don't like to gossip
about anyone behind their back!

1082
01:40:30,440 --> 01:40:33,640
We have a family! We'll have to
follow the norms of the society!

1083
01:40:34,080 --> 01:40:37,880
If she wants to live here
then refuse her, got it?

1084
01:40:38,680 --> 01:40:39,840
Ok, mother. Go in.

1085
01:40:41,240 --> 01:40:42,440
Kalyani!

1086
01:40:44,080 --> 01:40:47,560
Don't mind mother.

1087
01:40:48,280 --> 01:40:49,880
Where will you wander?

1088
01:40:50,000 --> 01:40:53,520
You're under my oath. Wait
here until my husband returns.

1089
01:40:53,960 --> 01:40:56,120
He'll definitely
arrange something for you.

1090
01:40:57,280 --> 01:40:59,600
Come.

1091
01:41:04,080 --> 01:41:05,920
We came here with a lot
of expectations, doctor.

1092
01:41:06,040 --> 01:41:08,960
What should we do now?
She's in trouble.

1093
01:41:09,160 --> 01:41:10,920
Look, Pratap, I would've
definitely done something..

1094
01:41:11,040 --> 01:41:13,040
..if it was possible.

1095
01:41:13,320 --> 01:41:16,680
There's no work in my nursing
home that I can assign to her.

1096
01:41:18,400 --> 01:41:24,960
But our maid is on leave. We
need a replacement for her..

1097
01:41:25,080 --> 01:41:29,440
..who could wash the patients'
clothes or clean their rooms.

1098
01:41:30,120 --> 01:41:31,640
Will she do all this?

1099
01:41:31,760 --> 01:41:36,280
No! She won't!
- I will.

1100
01:41:36,680 --> 01:41:38,720
I'll do everything.

1101
01:41:39,200 --> 01:41:42,480
I just need shelter right now.

1102
01:41:46,000 --> 01:41:47,720
I've heard your story from them.

1103
01:41:48,280 --> 01:41:50,680
For now, you can start working here.

1104
01:41:51,320 --> 01:41:54,040
I'll make the arrangements to
make you a trained nurse later.

1105
01:41:54,560 --> 01:41:56,000
Where will she stay?

1106
01:41:59,560 --> 01:42:00,840
Nurse.

1107
01:42:01,840 --> 01:42:02,920
Yes, doctor?

1108
01:42:03,200 --> 01:42:06,440
Show her the room on the terrace,
next to the storeroom.

1109
01:42:06,720 --> 01:42:08,960
She'll stay there.
- Yes, doctor.

1110
01:42:21,120 --> 01:42:22,720
This is your room.

1111
01:43:15,320 --> 01:43:18,520
You'll back answer me! - Oh gosh!
Will you beat me with this?

1112
01:43:18,640 --> 01:43:22,200
Yes! I'll kill you! Why did
you serve me tea in a dirty cup?

1113
01:43:22,480 --> 01:43:23,800
What happened?

1114
01:43:23,920 --> 01:43:25,360
You ask what happened!

1115
01:43:25,600 --> 01:43:27,880
This big hospital of
yours is filled..

1116
01:43:28,000 --> 01:43:30,960
..with illiterate
nurses and useless maids!

1117
01:43:32,080 --> 01:43:33,200
What did she do?

1118
01:43:33,320 --> 01:43:35,520
My husband has
brought new cups for me.

1119
01:43:35,640 --> 01:43:39,120
But she served me tea in
this dirty and broken cup!

1120
01:43:39,520 --> 01:43:44,120
Why? How would I know that
your husband brought.. - Shut up!

1121
01:43:44,440 --> 01:43:47,560
Did you hear? She's
arguing with me in your presence!

1122
01:43:47,840 --> 01:43:49,960
You leave. Don't get angry..

1123
01:43:50,080 --> 01:43:51,120
Oh, God!
- Sit!

1124
01:43:51,240 --> 01:43:52,760
I've never seen such a woman!

1125
01:43:52,880 --> 01:43:56,360
She's so hot-tempered!
She hit the cup on my face!

1126
01:43:56,480 --> 01:44:00,360
If you don't arrange for
a good maid immediately..

1127
01:44:00,680 --> 01:44:05,680
..then I'll break all the
furniture of your hospital!

1128
01:44:05,920 --> 01:44:10,360
Calm down. I'll make complete
arrangements for your service, ok?

1129
01:44:12,880 --> 01:44:14,200
Listen.

1130
01:44:20,400 --> 01:44:23,920
The patient in room no. 3
is suffering from hysteria.

1131
01:44:24,400 --> 01:44:26,720
She gets very angry.

1132
01:44:27,200 --> 01:44:29,560
None of our maids
are able to handle her.

1133
01:44:30,480 --> 01:44:35,360
After observing your work, I think
you know how to control patients.

1134
01:44:35,640 --> 01:44:37,840
If you could take
her responsibility..

1135
01:44:37,960 --> 01:44:40,160
Don't worry. I'll see.

1136
01:44:40,560 --> 01:44:41,720
Good.

1137
01:44:49,560 --> 01:44:52,400
What do you want?
- The doctor has sent me.

1138
01:44:54,160 --> 01:44:56,520
Are you a nurse?
- No. I'm a maid.

1139
01:44:56,640 --> 01:44:58,120
Maid!

1140
01:45:00,440 --> 01:45:02,800
What's your name?
- Kalyani.

1141
01:45:02,920 --> 01:45:07,080
They've chosen a nice name for you!

1142
01:45:08,480 --> 01:45:10,760
Are you married?
- No.

1143
01:45:11,160 --> 01:45:14,880
So you're a damsel!

1144
01:45:16,160 --> 01:45:18,240
That's why you've
adorned yourself so much!

1145
01:45:18,480 --> 01:45:21,720
Wonder what you'd do
if you were beautiful..

1146
01:45:21,840 --> 01:45:23,240
What am I supposed to do?

1147
01:45:24,720 --> 01:45:26,600
Massage my feet!

1148
01:45:27,680 --> 01:45:30,960
Get up, you fool! How
dare you sit on my bed?

1149
01:45:31,080 --> 01:45:35,240
I'm sorry.. - Shut up!
Go and wash this bed sheet!

1150
01:45:39,280 --> 01:45:40,400
And listen.

1151
01:45:42,280 --> 01:45:44,120
I have tea numerous times.

1152
01:45:44,320 --> 01:45:46,360
I should get tea on the dot, get it?

1153
01:45:46,480 --> 01:45:48,480
Yes. - Now leave.

1154
01:46:02,080 --> 01:46:03,920
Kalyani!

1155
01:46:17,320 --> 01:46:18,640
Kalyani!

1156
01:46:18,760 --> 01:46:20,400
Where the hell are you?

1157
01:46:22,760 --> 01:46:25,920
See, I've brought
flowers for you today!

1158
01:46:26,040 --> 01:46:30,640
You've bedecked yourself in
the morning and come to show-off!

1159
01:46:34,880 --> 01:46:37,040
There's no sugar in it!

1160
01:46:37,160 --> 01:46:39,960
I've brought sugar. You
can put as much you want.

1161
01:46:40,320 --> 01:46:43,640
Are you ordering me? Put sugar in it!

1162
01:46:49,960 --> 01:46:51,320
Mix it up!

1163
01:46:52,680 --> 01:46:54,000
Enough!

1164
01:46:56,160 --> 01:47:00,640
Where are you going?
Go and wash my clothes!

1165
01:47:11,120 --> 01:47:13,720
Wait! Open this window!

1166
01:47:46,840 --> 01:47:50,480
Shobha! Why did you arrive suddenly?

1167
01:47:52,560 --> 01:47:54,920
Why are you quiet?
- Kalyani..

1168
01:47:55,880 --> 01:47:59,040
You'll have to come to
Sadar hospital with me.

1169
01:47:59,800 --> 01:48:01,640
Hospital! What happened?

1170
01:48:01,920 --> 01:48:03,640
Your.. dad..

1171
01:48:05,760 --> 01:48:06,960
Dad!

1172
01:48:07,720 --> 01:48:08,880
Yes.

1173
01:48:10,080 --> 01:48:14,600
He came to my place,
searching for you.

1174
01:48:16,240 --> 01:48:18,600
He was coming here, but..

1175
01:48:19,440 --> 01:48:21,440
..he met with an accident on the way.

1176
01:48:24,800 --> 01:48:27,720
Recently his vision had become weak.

1177
01:48:29,960 --> 01:48:31,120
How is he now?

1178
01:48:32,320 --> 01:48:34,400
He's.. not fine.

1179
01:48:37,760 --> 01:48:39,040
Come on.

1180
01:48:48,440 --> 01:48:51,560
Sadashiv, who met with an accident
this morning, in which room is he?

1181
01:48:52,280 --> 01:48:53,600
Come.

1182
01:49:57,800 --> 01:49:59,560
Kalyani!

1183
01:50:03,480 --> 01:50:05,200
Kalyani!

1184
01:50:11,040 --> 01:50:13,080
Kalyani!

1185
01:50:15,760 --> 01:50:18,120
Can't you hear? She's calling you.

1186
01:50:20,760 --> 01:50:22,960
Kalyani!

1187
01:50:36,680 --> 01:50:40,400
My throat's paining calling you
out and you didn't even listen!

1188
01:50:41,680 --> 01:50:46,840
Wow! Look at her face, as if
she'll drop dead right now!

1189
01:50:48,480 --> 01:50:49,720
What do I have to do?

1190
01:50:49,840 --> 01:50:52,560
What do you mean? Did you
forget that it's time for my tea?

1191
01:50:52,840 --> 01:50:56,160
Where the hell were you?
Go and make two cups of tea.

1192
01:50:56,640 --> 01:50:57,920
My husband is coming here.

1193
01:50:59,120 --> 01:51:00,400
Wait!

1194
01:51:00,840 --> 01:51:02,360
Go and get my talc from there!

1195
01:51:12,680 --> 01:51:14,520
Listen.

1196
01:51:18,040 --> 01:51:21,960
Don't you dare come decked
up in front of my husband!

1197
01:51:32,640 --> 01:51:34,720
Why are you sitting away from me?

1198
01:51:35,320 --> 01:51:37,440
Why are you quiet? Answer me.

1199
01:51:37,920 --> 01:51:39,880
Don't you love me?

1200
01:51:42,120 --> 01:51:44,240
Who is it?

1201
01:51:45,800 --> 01:51:48,360
You! What are you doing here?

1202
01:51:48,480 --> 01:51:50,440
You were secretly
overhearing our conversation!

1203
01:51:50,560 --> 01:51:53,880
Shameless!
- What's the matter, Shivani?

1204
01:51:54,160 --> 01:51:56,200
Who're you getting angry on?
- You sit calmly!

1205
01:51:56,520 --> 01:51:59,640
She's a shameless maid!
I'll teach her a lesson today!

1206
01:51:59,720 --> 01:52:01,920
I'll complain to the
doctor about you!

1207
01:52:02,240 --> 01:52:05,400
I'll get you thrown
out of here! Get lost!

1208
01:52:35,200 --> 01:52:37,600
Kalyani!

1209
01:52:39,440 --> 01:52:41,440
You're still standing here!

1210
01:52:41,560 --> 01:52:43,360
The patient in room no.
3 is very furious!

1211
01:52:43,920 --> 01:52:45,600
Quickly take tea for her!

1212
01:52:46,360 --> 01:52:48,840
Just one cup. Her husband left.

1213
01:53:46,400 --> 01:53:48,440
Doctor!

1214
01:53:50,040 --> 01:53:52,160
No. 3!

1215
01:53:53,720 --> 01:53:56,160
Nurse!

1216
01:53:56,800 --> 01:54:00,040
How can you say this,
doctor? She used to be very happy.

1217
01:54:00,520 --> 01:54:03,600
When I was with her this evening,
she was absolutely fine.

1218
01:54:04,200 --> 01:54:08,120
What happened in this brief while
that caused her to commit suicide?

1219
01:54:09,200 --> 01:54:11,800
I think..
- What?

1220
01:54:13,320 --> 01:54:16,480
Sorry, but I feel this
isn't a case of suicide.

1221
01:54:17,560 --> 01:54:19,960
Someone killed her.
- Impossible.

1222
01:54:20,520 --> 01:54:23,240
No one can commit this
crime in my nursing home.

1223
01:54:23,840 --> 01:54:25,640
Why did you suspect this?

1224
01:54:26,040 --> 01:54:27,720
I can't be sure..

1225
01:54:28,160 --> 01:54:30,320
..but when I was
with her this evening..

1226
01:54:30,440 --> 01:54:34,560
..she fought with a maid
and scolded her a lot.

1227
01:54:34,960 --> 01:54:39,320
Some downtrodden maids do such
things for revenge sometimes.

1228
01:54:39,800 --> 01:54:43,800
Call that maid. I'll talk..
- She's right behind you.

1229
01:54:48,600 --> 01:54:52,120
Kalyani! You're.. here?

1230
01:54:53,720 --> 01:54:55,560
Move!

1231
01:54:55,800 --> 01:54:59,560
Doctor, is your
entire staff present here?

1232
01:54:59,760 --> 01:55:02,000
Yes.
- And Mrs. Shivani's husband?

1233
01:55:02,600 --> 01:55:04,120
Yes, he's Mr. Vikas.

1234
01:55:04,680 --> 01:55:06,360
Mr. Vikas, I'm very sorry.

1235
01:55:06,920 --> 01:55:09,000
What have you to say about this?
- What?

1236
01:55:09,960 --> 01:55:11,400
What have you to say about this?

1237
01:55:15,200 --> 01:55:18,880
Inspector, I think she
committed suicide. - No!

1238
01:55:19,000 --> 01:55:25,160
No! She didn't!
Murder! I murdered her!

1239
01:55:25,280 --> 01:55:28,560
Punish me! I killed her!

1240
01:55:28,680 --> 01:55:32,520
I killed her!

1241
01:55:33,080 --> 01:55:34,880
When I regained conscious..

1242
01:55:35,720 --> 01:55:37,880
..I realized that I had high fever.

1243
01:55:39,280 --> 01:55:42,400
In court, Dr. Verma
tried to prove that..

1244
01:55:43,520 --> 01:55:45,000
..while committing the crime..

1245
01:55:45,120 --> 01:55:48,640
..I was suffering through brain
fever and I wasn't in my senses.

1246
01:55:49,880 --> 01:55:53,640
That's why the judge
sentenced me to 8 years in jail.

1247
