embarrassed to meet him.

1249
01:56:03,880 --> 01:56:07,640
My crime was much bigger than his.

1250
01:56:09,680 --> 01:56:13,840
Jailor, this is my past.

1251
01:56:14,960 --> 01:56:20,240
Now you tell me. How can I
forget this and dream of my future?

1252
01:56:21,080 --> 01:56:24,320
How can I ruin a decent
man's unblemished life?

1253
01:56:24,400 --> 01:56:26,720
No, Mahesh. This is not possible.

1254
01:56:27,120 --> 01:56:32,200
