girl committed this crime.

1257
01:56:38,000 --> 01:56:40,920
Will she have to suffer all
her life for that one mistake?

1258
01:56:41,760 --> 01:56:44,760
If our society doesn't accept
such criminals with an open heart..

1259
01:56:45,200 --> 01:56:46,800
..then crime will
increase all the more.

1260
01:56:48,040 --> 01:56:50,520
Where will these
unfortunate people go?

1261
01:56:51,080 --> 01:56:55,840
Admit her in the ashram that
you've opened for such girls.

1262
01:56:56,400 --> 01:57:00,840
I thought the same, but
after knowing her past,

1263
01:57:01,120 --> 01:57:04,960
I'm sure that Devendra made no
mistake in choosing that girl.

1264
01:57:06,760 --> 01:57:09,080
Devendra is my only son.

1265
01:57:10,560 --> 01:57:12,720
I could never imagine..

1266
01:57:13,760 --> 01:57:17,600
